"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?32/11/32954/abstract/1\">",
"      Reaven GM. Banting lecture 1988. Role of insulin resistance in human disease. Diabetes 1988; 37:1595.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?32/11/32954/abstract/2\">",
